    <title>The tutorial of using the Surface firmware package.</title>
    <link href="/zh_TW/2022/07/31/SurfaceFirmwareUsage/"/>
    <url>/zh_TW/2022/07/31/SurfaceFirmwareUsage/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><font size=4>如果你的 Surface 設備在安裝更新後出現某些異常，或出現驅動缺失，你可以通過 Surface 韌件包來回滾更新。</font></p><p class="note note-primary"><font size=3>警告：<br/><br/>1. 在安裝韌體前接入電源適配器，並備份設備上所有重要的資料。 <br/><br/>2. 若要閱讀微軟官方文檔，訪問 <a href=“https://support.microsoft.com/zh-tw/surface/下載適用於-surface-的驅動程式和韌體-09bb2e09-2a4b-cb69-0951-078a7739e120”><u>下下載適用於 Surface 的驅動程式和韌體</u></a>。 並且停止閱讀本文中的內容。 <br/><br/>3. 如果你曾使用公版 Windows 映射安裝作業系統，那麼某些固件即使在安裝韌體包後將仍然處於缺失狀態。</font></p><br/><br/><p><font size=6>第一步</font></p><p><font size=2>確認你的作業系統版本</font></p><br/><p><font size=4><ul><li>同時按下 <b>Windows 鍵</b> 和 <b>R 鍵</b>。 </li><li>在彈出的視窗中鍵入 <b>Winver</b>。 </li><li>你將看到 <b>關於 Windows</b> 視窗。紅色標記處顯示了系統版本資訊。 </li><br/><div class="imgWinver"><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lzj20021216/resource/main/DownloadSurfaceFirmware/Winver.jpg"/></div><br/><style>    .imgWinver{        text-align:center;    }</style><li>將窗口擱置到一邊，不要將其關閉。</li></ul></font></p><br/><br/><p><font size=6>第二步</font></p><p><font size=2>下載韌體包</font></p><br/><p><font size=4>根據你的 Surface 型號，在瀏覽器中打開對應的連結。 <br/>Surface 韌件清單：<br/><br/><p><b>Surface Pro 系列</b></p><table><thead><tr><th align="center">型號</th><th align="center">下載連結</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">Surface Pro 8</td><td align="center"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=103503">https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=103503</a></td></tr><tr><td align="center">Surface Pro 7+ 和 擁有 LTE 模組的 Surface Pro 7+</td><td align="center"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=102633">https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=102633</a></td></tr><tr><td align="center">Surface Pro 7</td><td align="center"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=100419">https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=100419</a></td></tr><tr><td align="center">Surface Pro 6</td><td align="center"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=57514">https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=57514</a></td></tr><tr><td align="center">擁有 LTE 模組的 Surface Pro （第五代）</td><td align="center"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=56278">https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=56278</a></td></tr><tr><td align="center">Surface Pro (第五代)</td><td align="center"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=55484">https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=55484</a></td></tr><tr><td align="center">Surface Pro 4</td><td align="center"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=49498">https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=49498</a></td></tr><tr><td align="center">Surface Pro 3</td><td align="center"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=38826">https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=38826</a></td></tr><tr><td align="center">Surface Pro 2</td><td align="center"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=49042">https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=49042</a></td></tr><tr><td align="center">Surface Pro</td><td align="center"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=49038">https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=49038</a></td></tr></tbody></table><br/><hr><br/><p><b>Surface Book 系列</b></p><table><thead><tr><th align="center">型號</th><th align="center">下載連結</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">Surface Book</td><td align="center"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=49497">https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=49497</a></td></tr><tr><td align="center">Surface Book 2</td><td align="center"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=56261">https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=56261</a></td></tr><tr><td align="center">Surface Book 3</td><td align="center"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=101315">https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=101315</a></td></tr></tbody></table><br/><hr><br/><p><b>Surface Laptop 系列</b></p><table><thead><tr><th align="center">型號</th><th align="center">下載連結</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">Surface Laptop Studio</td><td align="center"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=103505">https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=103505</a></td></tr><tr><td align="center">Surface Laptop Go 2</td><td align="center">尚未發佈</td></tr><tr><td align="center">Surface Laptop Go</td><td align="center"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=102261">https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=102261</a></td></tr><tr><td align="center">Surface Laptop 4 （Intel 處理器）</td><td align="center"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=102924">https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=102924</a></td></tr><tr><td align="center">Surface Laptop 4 （AMD 處理器）</td><td align="center"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=102923">https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=102923</a></td></tr><tr><td align="center">Surface Laptop 3（Intel 處理器）</td><td align="center"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=100429">https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=100429</a></td></tr><tr><td align="center">Surface Laptop 3 （AMD 處理器）</td><td align="center"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=100428">https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=100428</a></td></tr><tr><td align="center">Surface Laptop 2</td><td align="center"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=57515">https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=57515</a></td></tr><tr><td align="center">Surface Laptop (第一代)</td><td align="center"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=55489">https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=55489</a></td></tr></tbody></table><br/><hr><br/><p><b>Surface Go 系列</b></p><table><thead><tr><th align="center">型號</th><th align="center">下載連結</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">Surface Go 3</td><td align="center"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=103504">https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=103504</a></td></tr><tr><td align="center">Surface Go 2 和 擁有 LTE 模組的 Surface Go 2</td><td align="center"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=101304">https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=101304</a></td></tr><tr><td align="center">Surface Go</td><td align="center"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=57439">https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=57439</a></td></tr><tr><td align="center">擁有 LTE 模組的 Surface Go</td><td align="center"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=57601">https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=57601</a> (在退出 S 模式前，請勿下載 *.msi 格式的安裝檔。)</td></tr></tbody></table><br/><hr><br/><p><b>Surface Studio Series</b></p><table><thead><tr><th align="center">型號</th><th align="center">下載連結</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">Surface Studio 2</td><td align="center"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=57593">https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=57593</a></td></tr><tr><td align="center">Surface Studio (第一代)</td><td align="center"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=54311">https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=54311</a></td></tr></tbody></table><br/><hr><br/><p><b>其它型號</b></p><table><thead><tr><th align="center">型號</th><th align="center">下載連結</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">Surface 3 (Wi-Fi 版)</td><td align="center"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=49040">https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=49040</a></td></tr><tr><td align="center">Surface 3 (帶有 AT&amp;T 合約的 4G LTE 版)</td><td align="center"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=49039">https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=49039</a></td></tr><tr><td align="center">Surface 3 (帶有 Verizon 合約的 4G LTE 版)</td><td align="center"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=49920">https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=49920</a></td></tr><tr><td align="center">Surface 3 （無合約的 4G LTE 版） 以及北美地區銷售的非 AT&amp;T 合約機</td><td align="center"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=49037">https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=49037</a></td></tr><tr><td align="center">Surface 3 （帶有 Y！mobile 合約的 4G LTE 版） 以及北美地區以外銷售的 Surface 3 （4G LTE 版）</td><td align="center"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=49041">https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=49041</a></td></tr><tr><td align="center">Surface Hub 2</td><td align="center"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=101974">https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=101974</a></td></tr><tr><td align="center">Surface RT</td><td align="center">運行 Windows RT 作業系統的設備僅可透過 Windows Update 獲取和安裝更新。</td></tr></tbody></table><br/><hr><br/><p><b>配件</b></p><table><thead><tr><th align="center">型號</th><th align="center">下載連結</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">Surface Dock 和 Surface Dock 2</td><td align="center"><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=101317">https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?id=101317</a></td></tr></tbody></table><br/><hr><br/></font></p><p><font size=4><ul><li>點擊頁面上的 <b>Donwload</b> 按鈕。</li><br/><div class="imgDownloadPage1"><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lzj20021216/resource/main/DownloadSurfaceFirmware/DownloadPage1.jpg"/></div><br/><style>    .imgDownloadPage1{        text-align:center;    }</style><li>打開剛才的 <b>關於 Windows</b> 視窗，然後根據其中的系統版本資訊選擇下載物件。</li><br/><div class="imgDownloadPage2"><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lzj20021216/resource/main/DownloadSurfaceFirmware/DownloadPage2.jpg"/></div><br/><style>    .imgDownloadPage2{        text-align:center;    }</style><li>下載完成後，運行安裝程式，按照提示操作即可。</li></ul><p></font></p></p>]]></content>
    
    
